    "Public Records",
    "Visible Identification"
  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "By January 1, 2027, requires each law enforcement agency operating in the State to maintain a publicly available policy on the visible identification of law enforcement officers.  Adds law enforcement officers to covered public servants who may request any government agency, person, or organization to not make publicly available on the Internet certain covered personal information."
    }
  ],
